WEBVTT

00:00:54.280 --> 00:00:55.039
A Hai

00:00:55.359 --> 00:00:57.119
You dare rob on my turf?

00:00:57.840 --> 00:00:59.200
You're looking for death.

00:01:05.040 --> 00:01:05.719
A Zhan

00:01:12.519 --> 00:01:13.480
Zhao Qishan

00:01:18.840 --> 00:01:20.239
So beautiful.

00:01:22.840 --> 00:01:23.840
Have another glass.

00:01:24.280 --> 00:01:24.680
Drink up.

00:01:27.760 --> 00:01:28.959
I'm taking it all!

00:01:29.680 --> 00:01:30.519
Pay up.

00:01:32.120 --> 00:01:32.959
You just didn't see

00:01:32.959 --> 00:01:34.280
how amazing we were back then.

00:01:35.920 --> 00:01:36.200
Come on.

00:01:37.120 --> 00:01:37.840
One more time.

00:01:41.920 --> 00:01:43.480
Is it your turn to play?

00:01:44.120 --> 00:01:44.959
Hurry up, play, play.

00:01:45.920 --> 00:01:47.000
Do you want it or not?

00:01:47.920 --> 00:01:49.439
Show your hand.

00:01:51.000 --> 00:01:52.920
Pay up, pay up.

00:01:59.400 --> 00:02:00.519
Deal, deal the cards.

00:02:00.519 --> 00:02:01.680
Again, again, again.

00:02:02.480 --> 00:02:04.359
Good, Brother San, Brother San.

00:02:04.359 --> 00:02:05.879
Brother Hai, Brother Hai.

00:02:06.840 --> 00:02:07.319
Brother San.

00:02:07.599 --> 00:02:09.000
Continue, keep going.

00:02:10.080 --> 00:02:11.879
I'll definitely win this time.

00:02:11.879 --> 00:02:13.039
Come, I'll take him on.

00:02:14.000 --> 00:02:14.680
Good.

00:02:14.800 --> 00:02:15.560
Quick, quick, place your bets.

00:02:15.560 --> 00:02:16.759
You're confident, huh?

00:02:17.280 --> 00:02:18.759
I'll go first, come on.

00:02:22.879 --> 00:02:24.400
Is that all you have?

00:02:26.280 --> 00:02:27.159
Drink, drink, drink.

00:02:27.319 --> 00:02:28.360
Drink up.

00:02:28.879 --> 00:02:29.680
Honestly...

00:02:31.039 --> 00:02:32.039
How did this happen?

00:02:32.360 --> 00:02:33.199
A Zhan is dead.

00:02:34.319 --> 00:02:34.879
Uncle.

00:02:35.879 --> 00:02:36.400
Brother.

00:02:36.840 --> 00:02:38.159
Zhao Qishan killed someone.

00:02:38.319 --> 00:02:39.120
A life has been taken.

00:02:39.120 --> 00:02:40.520
We can't let him stay here.

00:02:40.680 --> 00:02:41.800
What if he attracts the police?

00:02:44.680 --> 00:02:46.199
He killed someone.

00:02:47.199 --> 00:02:48.319
How cruel.

00:02:53.319 --> 00:02:55.159
What does A Shan say?

00:02:57.120 --> 00:02:58.360
A Qiang has a great touch.

00:02:58.800 --> 00:02:59.479
One last time.

00:02:59.479 --> 00:03:00.159
You today...

00:03:00.879 --> 00:03:02.159
Playing even when you can't afford to lose.

00:03:02.800 --> 00:03:04.240
If you don't believe me, let's play another hand.

00:03:05.479 --> 00:03:06.199
What's going on?

00:03:06.520 --> 00:03:07.400
What is happening?

00:03:08.159 --> 00:03:08.840
This is...

00:03:19.080 --> 00:03:21.879
Everyone here was taken in by me.

00:03:22.360 --> 00:03:25.319
Isn't this a bit against the rules?

00:03:26.080 --> 00:03:26.879
Rules?

00:03:28.919 --> 00:03:29.560
Here,

00:03:30.319 --> 00:03:31.120
I only answer to you.

00:03:58.599 --> 00:03:59.520
A Shan.

00:03:59.960 --> 00:04:01.680
You've been too flashy lately.

00:04:02.400 --> 00:04:03.840
Forgot what I told you?

00:04:04.360 --> 00:04:06.680
Shady business shouldn't be too flashy.

00:04:07.159 --> 00:04:08.199
It will cause trouble.

00:04:14.719 --> 00:04:15.400
A Shan.

00:04:20.120 --> 00:04:20.639
The Boss.

00:04:21.800 --> 00:04:23.439
Someone owes me a few million.

00:04:23.439 --> 00:04:24.160
He ran away.

00:04:24.560 --> 00:04:25.399
Go take care of it for me.

00:04:27.160 --> 00:04:27.639
Okay.

00:04:39.800 --> 00:04:40.920
This final lesson,

00:04:41.399 --> 00:04:42.959
I hope it serves you well in the next life.

00:04:49.319 --> 00:04:50.800
The Boss, good morning.

00:05:22.079 --> 00:05:22.920
The Boss.

00:05:24.120 --> 00:05:25.920
Thank you for raising me all these years.

00:05:30.920 --> 00:05:31.720
A Shan.

00:05:32.279 --> 00:05:34.120
I knew I didn't misjudge you.

00:06:06.959 --> 00:06:07.439
So...

00:06:08.120 --> 00:06:09.480
Zhao Qishan is so scary.

00:06:11.399 --> 00:06:13.079
Then let's follow this story

00:06:14.519 --> 00:06:15.720
and talk more about Tan Tian.

00:06:19.199 --> 00:06:20.199
Congratulations, Brother San.

00:06:20.199 --> 00:06:21.319
Congrats, Brother San.

00:06:21.600 --> 00:06:22.560
The old man is gone.

00:06:22.759 --> 00:06:24.519
From now on, it's your world.

00:06:26.040 --> 00:06:27.439
The old man was too timid.

00:06:27.600 --> 00:06:28.720
Couldn't handle big business.

00:06:29.959 --> 00:06:31.079
I've always believed in you.

00:06:31.319 --> 00:06:32.519
I've been waiting for this day.

00:06:34.800 --> 00:06:35.439
You go ahead.

00:06:39.519 --> 00:06:40.199
Brother Tian.

00:06:41.000 --> 00:06:41.480
Brother Tian.

00:06:46.439 --> 00:06:47.759
If you want to make big money,

00:06:48.120 --> 00:06:49.000
you gotta have guts.

00:06:49.439 --> 00:06:51.279
You don't need to teach my brother about guts.

00:06:51.680 --> 00:06:52.879
We hate trouble.

00:06:53.319 --> 00:06:53.759
Get to the point.

00:06:55.480 --> 00:06:56.199
Brother San.

00:06:57.199 --> 00:06:58.399
Can't control your own brother?

00:07:04.879 --> 00:07:05.759
Let's hear it.

00:07:10.560 --> 00:07:12.160
You need a partner.

00:07:14.720 --> 00:07:16.639
I know a "pig" recently arrived in Taicheng.

00:07:20.000 --> 00:07:20.879
Let's pull a job together.

00:07:24.319 --> 00:07:26.480
You'll see the value in working with me.

00:07:30.120 --> 00:07:31.079
When do we start?

00:07:32.720 --> 00:07:33.720
Right now.

00:08:21.199 --> 00:08:22.279
Let's begin, you two.

00:08:34.399 --> 00:08:35.120
Mr. Park.

00:08:36.159 --> 00:08:37.279
Given your net worth,

00:08:37.919 --> 00:08:40.240
five million dollars for your life

00:08:40.559 --> 00:08:41.480
isn't expensive, is it?

00:08:43.279 --> 00:08:45.600
Your family is very worried about your safety.

00:08:46.000 --> 00:08:48.080
Say a few words to reassure them.

00:08:48.360 --> 00:08:49.120
Hello? Hello?

00:08:50.000 --> 00:08:50.960
As agreed,

00:08:51.320 --> 00:08:53.000
I'll let you hear your husband's voice.

00:08:53.399 --> 00:08:54.240
To make sure

00:08:54.639 --> 00:08:55.519
he's still alive.

00:08:55.639 --> 00:08:57.000
Honey! Honey!

00:08:58.000 --> 00:08:58.399
Honey!

00:08:58.759 --> 00:08:59.399
Save me!

00:08:59.480 --> 00:09:00.240
Give them the money!

00:09:00.320 --> 00:09:01.120
It's me. I don't want to die.

00:09:01.120 --> 00:09:01.519
Okay.

00:09:08.879 --> 00:09:09.799
The money...

00:09:10.879 --> 00:09:12.879
We got the money.

00:09:13.840 --> 00:09:15.799
I guarantee no one will find the body.